							</a>
						</h1>
					</header><section class="summary cf" itemprop="description" aria-labelledby="hp_news_article_6_title"><p>
								Attention Hallettsville ISD Parents/Guardians:<br>Hallettsville ISD is releasing a website to help compile all of Hallettsville ISD’s Covid-19 resources in one location.  The site includes many items such as:<br>·         Campus specific resources with weekly lesson updates from staff and suggested schedules.<br>·         A repository of all communications put out at the district level regarding the Covid-19 pandemic.<br>·         Library resources with username and login information.<br>·         Food service information and the link to sign up for meal packages.<br>·         Technology help desk contact information.<br>·         Local free WiFi hotspots.<br>·         A staff email directory if you need to get in touch with a teacher or administrator.<br><br>To access the site go to: <br>https://sites.google.com/hisdbrahmas.org/hisdcovid19/  or https://bit.ly/3aWnY8J<br><br>Check back regularly for updates and new information.
							</p>
						</section></article><article id="hp_news_article_7" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_7_title">
